WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.360
Men will be like, oh,

00:00:01.361 --> 00:00:03.161
I love how you're always glowing.

00:00:03.162 --> 00:00:06.141
You look so beautiful the second you put on lotion.

00:00:06.200 --> 00:00:08.200
They're like, Ew, gross.

00:00:08.201 --> 00:00:11.081
You're all slimy. Why do you think I'm always glowing?

00:00:11.082 --> 00:00:14.721
It isn't magic. It takes work to be this glowy.

00:00:14.722 --> 00:00:16.241
In fact, come over here,

00:00:16.242 --> 00:00:18.201
because I think you're looking really dry.

00:00:18.202 --> 00:00:20.721
Oh, like it's the end of the freaking world.

00:00:20.722 --> 00:00:24.323
Guys wouldn't do anything but put lotion on themselves.
